---
---
<section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">Funnels & Automation Packages</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        From planning a single lead magnet to building complex Kajabi launch flows.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">

      {/* Package 1 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-[#77BA55]/50 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-2">Funnel Strategy Map</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Best for creators and businesses that need a clear funnel plan before building.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">
          <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500 block mb-1">Starting from</span>
          $500
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow">
          {['Funnel audit or planning call', 'Offer journey map', 'Lead magnet path', 'Email sequence outline', 'Checkout/access flow map', 'Automation recommendations'].map(feature => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#77BA55] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="block w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[#27496D] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
          Book Free Funnel Audit
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* Package 2 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-[#77BA55]/50 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-2">Lead Funnel Setup</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Best for clients who need a lead magnet, opt-in page, form flow, and welcome sequence.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">
          <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500 block mb-1">Starting from</span>
          $1,200
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow">
          {['Opt-in page structure', 'Lead magnet delivery flow', 'Form setup guidance', 'Welcome email sequence', 'Basic tagging/segmentation plan', 'Testing checklist'].map(feature => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#77BA55] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="block w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[#27496D] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
          Book Free Funnel Audit
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* Package 3 */}
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#27496D] p-8 flex flex-col relative shadow-md">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-[#27496D] text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">
          Popular
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-2">Course Launch Funnel Build</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Best for creators and educators launching a course, cohort, or membership.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">
          <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500 block mb-1">Starting from</span>
          $2,500
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow">
          {['Landing/sales page structure', 'Offer and checkout flow', 'Launch email sequence', 'Lead nurture sequence', 'Student onboarding sequence', 'Automation map', 'Launch QA checklist'].map(feature => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#77BA55] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="block w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-[#77BA55] rounded-xl hover:bg-[#65A344] transition-colors shadow-sm">
          Book Free Funnel Audit
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">

      {/* Package 4 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-[#77BA55]/50 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-2">Kajabi Funnel & Automation Build</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Best for clients who want Kajabi pages, offers, checkout, and automations connected.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">
          <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500 block mb-1">Custom quote, usually from</span>
          $4,000
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow">
          {['Kajabi funnel setup support', 'Landing pages & Offers', 'Email campaigns & Automations', 'Tags and access flow', 'Student onboarding', 'QA and launch support'].map(feature => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#77BA55] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="block w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[#27496D] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
          Book Free Funnel Audit
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* Package 5 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-[#77BA55]/50 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-2">Monthly Funnel Support</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Best for existing businesses that need ongoing updates, launches, and maintenance.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#27496D] mb-6">
          <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500 block mb-1">Starting from</span>
          $600<span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500">/month</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow">
          {['Funnel updates', 'Email updates', 'Automation review', 'Launch support', 'Student onboarding improvements', 'Reporting review support'].map(feature => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#77BA55] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="block w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[#27496D] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
          Book Free Funnel Audit
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 text-sm text-slate-600 text-center">
      <p>
        <strong>Note:</strong> Final quote depends on funnel complexity, number of pages, email sequence length, platform setup, automations, review rounds, integrations, and launch requirements. Every project starts with a free audit so we can recommend the right scope before you pay.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
